Path Recruitment Message 1

Date: 02/02/2023

We invite you to join us, The Path, in our quest for a better future. Under the leadership of Mega Gold, we are a team of evolved apes determined to protect our kind and fight against the oppressive regime of Doc Gibbons and his Mega Mutant allies.

We believe that by standing together and using our unique abilities, we can create a world where all mutants are free to live and thrive. We are looking for brave and dedicated individuals who are ready to fight for our cause and make a difference.

Join us and become part of a movement that is changing the future. The Path is the way to a better tomorrow.

Together, we are unstoppable.

Join us and be a part of The Path.
